Nanette Fabray (October 27, 1920 – February 22, 2018) was an American actress and comedian. She began acting around age 3. Fabray starred in many movies and television programs. She was aunt of actress and singer Shelley Fabares. Nanette Fabray was born in San Diego, California.
Fabray died at her home in Palos Verdes, California on February 22, 2018 of natural causes at the age of 97.
